Package Characters

Class Monster

java.lang.Object
Characters.GameCharacter
Characters.Monster
public class Monster extends GameCharacter
Monster is a class that represents a monster character in the game. It extends the Character class and has methods to move the monster towards the Cyborg or move randomly.
